So, I'll make a motion to accept the minutes of the February meeting.

12
00:00:40,262 --> 00:00:40,302
2nd.

13
00:00:41,964 --> 00:00:42,604
All in favor?

14
00:00:43,344 --> 00:00:43,785
Aye.

15
